The paper deals with the problem of clustering, which is a fundamental topic in machine learning and data analysis. The algorithms introduced in the paper are based on belief propagation, spectral methods, and information theory, which are all common techniques in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
